    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581170/extras/aea78713dc58c15f5502762e9a33ad1c.avif?t=1725016724\" width=600 height=136 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581170/extras/bc00c466f53166baca58526c197c9890.avif?t=1725016724\" width=600 height=299 /></span><br><br>这是个尚未有文明存在的新世界。<br><br>在这个尚不存在文明的世界上，<br>有位造物主──也就是「你」，<br>和一位有着神话中女神之名，被称为「神托少女」的少女。<br><br>你和少女将同心协力，共享欢笑、泪水以及喜悦，<br>并一步步培育出文明。<br><br>百年后的世界究竟会是什么模样？<br>欢迎身为玩家的你亲自体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581170/extras/0c87a581b1362cd1838cd67daa51fa4c.avif?t=1725016724\" width=600 height=136 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581170/extras/7fc10c83792bd424d1d7aa7734168e35.avif?t=1725016724\" width=600 height=298 /></span><br><br>・本游戏是简单易玩的回合制模拟游戏。玩家透过建筑与开拓等方式，在百年间培育出文明。<br>・你将和被称为「神托巫女」，与神话中地母神同名的少女一起培育文明。<br>・游戏中不会有外交、战争或灾害等负面又复杂的要素。<br>・你的文明不会被蛮族入侵，也不会被甘地用核弹攻击。<br>・你可以随心所欲，自由地培育属于自己的文明。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581170/extras/f5a769cef652f5a2f77fbdda452fe545.avif?t=1725016724\" width=600 height=136 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1581170/extras/df20fdfd1d40379eaefb1c585e0d4f59.avif?t=1725016724\" width=600 height=298 /></span><br><br>在《百年王国》里，你将会创造出各式各样的世界，并培育出文明。<br>无论是拥有群山峻岭、辽阔大海，<br>或是一望无际草原的绿意盎然世界，都由你随心所欲创造与培育。",
